                   ORB GLOBES -- BLOCKERS OF EVIL                               Legend states that one cannot destroy a rainbow pool, for it hath a strange     magnetic field around it which dost prevent interaction. Apparently, certain    mysterious orbs exist, which when placed around the pool, disable the field.    END                                                                             This could enable one to then do whatever he is attempting to do to the pool,   as the field will no longer stop him.                                           FINISH                                                                          